    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Raw Energy balls"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<span><i class=\"fa fa-book\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/recipe-category/sweets-and-cakes/\" rel=\"tag\">Sweets and Cakes</a></span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "May 1, 2015<span class=\"value-title\" title=\"2015-05-01\"></span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "Melt in your mouth sweetness from the dates and creaminess from the nuts and the almond butter. Great sustaining energy with a cacao kick!"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Prep: 20 min",
        "20 min 20 min"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Ingredients"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">almonds or walnuts, activated and dehydrated if possible</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">medjool dates, pitted</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/4 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">desiccated coconut</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 tbsp</span> <span class=\"name\">raw cacao</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\"> tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">cinnamon</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/4 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">almond butter</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Directions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>In a food processor or strong blender grind the almonds or walnuts until finely ground."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>Add the dates, coconut shreds and spices and grind into a fine meal."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>Add the almond butter and process again until thoroughly mixed. If too dry add either a few drops of water or some melted coconut oil."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>Form into small balls and roll in shredded coconut. Store in a sealed container on the counter for up to 3 days, or refrigerate for up to a few weeks."
    },
